Lee ya wallafa littafinsa mai suna "Al Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order" tare da Houghton Mifflin Harcourt a wannan watan kuma shi ne Babban Jami'in Kamfanin Sinovation Ventures, wanda ya zuba jari a daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin kera kere na kasar Sin, Face++.
