Ana gudanar da taron ne a Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, taron na yau da dare na iya kawo magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma samun labaran Pittsburgh, a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne Trump zai ziyarci West Virginia karo na biyu a cikin watan da ya gabata, jihar da ta samu karin kashi 40 a shekarar 2016.
