Koriya ta Arewa ta ce ba za ta amince da yarjejeniyar ba tare da amincewa ba
A ranar Asabar, ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa tsauraran takunkumin na kara tsananta wa Amurka kuma ba za ta kawar da makaman nukiliyarta baki daya ba a irin wannan yanayi.
Ri Yong Ho ya shaida wa babban taron shekara-shekara na kungiyar ta duniya cewa Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "matakai masu kyau" a cikin shekarar da ta gabata, kamar dakatar da atisayen nukiliya da kuma harkokin sadarwa, dakatar da gwajin nukiliya, da kuma yin alkawarin ba da damar yada makaman nukiliya ko fasahar nukiliya.
Amma, ba mu ga irin wannan martani daga Amurka ba,'in ji ta.
Ba tare da amincewa da Amurka ba za a sami amincewa a cikin tsaron ƙasarmu ba kuma a irin wannan yanayi ba za mu iya hana kanmu ba da farko.
Duk da cewa Ri ya maimaita korafin da Koriya ta Arewa ta saba da shi game da adawar Washington da matakin tsauraran matakai na nukiliya wanda za a ba Koriya ta Arewa lada idan ta dauki matakai na tsauraran matakai, sanarwar ta kasance mai mahimmanci saboda ba ta musanta nukiliya ba gaba daya kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya yi magana ne game da sanarwar hadin gwiwa tsakanin Kim John-un da Donald Trump a taron farko tsakanin shugaban Amurka na yanzu da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa a Singapore a ranar 12 ga Yuni, inda Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki kan "yantar da yankin Koriya ta Kudu" yayin da Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbatar da tsaron Koriya.
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi kokarin kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, amma Amurka ta ce dole ne Pyongyang ta fara kawar da makaman nukiliyarta.
Washington ta kuma yi watsi da kiran da ake yi na sassauta takunkumin da kasashen duniya suka kakaba wa Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta bukaci a fara 'yantar da nukiliya' kuma tana kara matsa lamba ta hanyar takunkumi don cimma burinta ta hanyar tilastawa, har ma tana adawa da sanarwar kawo karshen yakin", in ji RI.
Yadda takunkumi zai iya cinye mu shine mafarkin mutanen da basu san komai game da mu ba.
Amma matsalar ita ce, tsauraran takunkumi na ci gaba da kara mana rashin imani.
Ri bai ambaci wani shiri ba na taron karawa juna sani tsakanin Kim da Trump, wanda shugaban ya sanar a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya mako daya da ta gabata.
Maimakon haka, ministan ya ambaci ganawa uku tsakanin Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in a cikin makonni biyar da suka gabata kuma ya kara da cewa: "Idan Koriya ta Kudu ce ta kasance jam'iyyar da ke kan batun hana nukiliya ba Amurka ba, to, hana nukiliya a yankin Koriya ba zai haifar da irin wannan halin da ba zai yiwu ba".
Duk da haka, jawabin Ri ya bambanta da na bara, lokacin da ya gaya wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa ba za a iya hana Amurka ta kai hari kan Koriya ta Arewa ba bayan da Shugaba Trump ya kira Kim "mai amfani da makamai masu linzami" a kan wani yunƙuri na kai-da-kai.
A wannan shekara a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Trump, wanda a bara ya yi barazanar lalata Koriya ta Arewa gaba daya, ya yaba wa Kim saboda ƙarfin hali da ya nuna wajen daukar matakan hana ta yin amfani da makaman nukiliya, amma ya ce akwai sauran aiki da yawa da za a yi kuma dole ne a dakatar da takunkumin har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta daina amfani da makaman nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce ba shi da wani takamaiman lokacin da zai yi hakan, ya ce ko zai ɗauki shekaru biyu, shekaru uku ko watanni biyar - ba kome.
China da Rasha na jayayya cewa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kamata ta ba Pyongyang lada saboda matakan da aka dauka.
Amma, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya fadawa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Alhamis: "Dole ne a aiwatar da takunkumin Majalisar Tsaro cikin tsauri kuma ba tare da wata matsala ba har sai mun cimma kuma mun tabbatar da kammala aikin hana yaduwar nukiliya.
Kwamitin Tsaro ya kara takunkumi kan Koriya ta Arewa baki daya a 2006 don kokarin takaita kudade ga shirye-shiryen nukiliya da kuma harkokin sadarwa na Pyongyang.
Ri ya gana da Pompeo a gaban Majalisar Dinkin Duniya sannan ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekarar, amma ziyarar ta ƙarshe ba ta tafi daidai ba.#
Pyongyang ta bar kasar a watan Yuli tana mai cewa an samu ci gaba, amma Koriya ta Arewa ta zarge ta cikin 'yan sa'o'i na yin umarni a matsayin dan daba.
Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin ganawa da Moon a wannan watan don kawar da tashar jirgi da tashar nukiliya idan Amurka ta dauki matakan da suka dace.
Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa cewa "Matakan da suka dace" da ya nemi su ne tabbacin tsaro da Trump ya bayar a Singapore da kuma motsi zuwa daidaita dangantaka da Amurka.
Harvard dalibai samun hanya samun isasshen hutu
Wani sabon darasi a Jami'ar Harvard a wannan shekara yana karantar da dalibai su kara yin barci domin magance al'adar macho na karatun dare da dare tare da shan maganin kafeyin.
Masana kimiyya sun gano cewa ɗalibai a manyan jami'o'i a duniya sukan yi wa kansu wa'azi.
Charles Czeisler, farfesa a likitancin bacci a Harvard Medical School kuma kwararre ne a asibitin Brigham da Women's wanda ya tsara wannan kwas, wanda ya yi imanin shine na farko a Amurka.
An yi wahayi zuwa gare shi a farkon karatun bayan ya ba da lacca game da tasirin rashin bacci akan ilmantarwa.
A ƙarshen darasin, wata yarinya ta zo wurina ta ce, "Me ya sa na soma sanin wannan a shekarata ta ƙarshe?"
Ya ce babu wanda ya gaya masa game da mahimmancin bacci - abin mamaki ne a gare ni,'in ji Telegraph.
Wannan kwas ɗin, wanda aka gabatar a karon farko a wannan shekara, ya bayyana wa ɗalibai yadda kyawawan halaye na barci ke taimakawa aikin ilimi da wasanni, da kuma inganta lafiyarsu gaba ɗaya.
Paul Barreira, farfesa a fannin tabin hankali a Harvard Medical School kuma darektan zartarwa na ayyukan kiwon lafiya na jami'ar, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da karatun ne bayan gano cewa dalibai suna fama da rashin bacci sosai a cikin mako.
Wannan darasi na awa ɗaya ya ƙunshi jerin ayyuka masu ma'amala.
A cikin wani sashe akwai hoto na ɗakin kwana, inda ɗalibai ke danna kofi, takalma da littattafai don koyi game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske da kuma yadda rashin barci ke shafar aikin wasanni, da kuma muhimmancin kyawawan halaye na barci.
A wani sashe kuma, masu halartar taron sun koyi yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci ke ƙara haɗarin ciwon zuciya, bugun jini, baƙin ciki da kuma ciwon daji.
Bayan haka, taswirar harabar, tare da gumakan hulɗa, yana ƙarfafa mahalarta suyi tunani game da al'adunsu na yau da kullun.
Mun san cewa hakan ba zai canja halayen ɗaliban nan da nan ba.
Amma muna ganin suna da hakkin sanin hakan - kamar yadda kai ma kake da hakkin sanin yadda shan taba yake shafar lafiyarka",in ji Farfesa Chesler.
Ya ce al'adun da ke nuna alfahari da kasancewa a farke duk dare na ci gaba, ya kara da cewa fasahar zamani da karuwar matsin lamba ga dalibai na nufin rashin bacci matsala ce mai tsanani.
Ya ce, tabbatar da cewa kuna samun isasshen barci mai kyau ya kamata ya zama hanya ga dalibai su magance damuwa, gajiya da damuwa - har ma su guji matsa lamba, domin rashin barci yana sa kwakwalwarka ta gaskata cewa kana barci, yana sa ka yi sanyi a kowane lokaci.
Raymond So, wani ɗan shekara 19 daga California wanda ke nazarin ilimin kimiyyar halitta da kimiyyar lissafi, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Chesler wajen tsara wannan hanya, bayan ya halarci ɗayan karatunsa a shekarar da ta gabata a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard.
Ya ce wannan darasi ya bude idanunsa kuma ya karfafa shi ya yi kokarin samun darasi ga dukkan harabar makarantar.
Muna fatan cewa mataki na gaba zai zama buƙatar duk ɗaliban sakandare su kammala irin wannan shirin karatun kafin su shiga ƙungiyar gasa.
Farfesa Ceisler ya ba da shawarar cewa ɗalibai suyi la'akari da kafa ƙararrawa don yin bacci, tare da farkawa, kuma su san illolin tasirin haske mai haske wanda allon lantarki da hasken LED ke fitarwa, wanda zai iya shafar tsarin motsin ku wanda ke haifar da matsalolin bacci.
Livingston 1-0 Rangers: kwallon Menga ta doke mutanen Gerrard
Rangers sun sha wahala wani mummunan wasa a gida yayin da Dolly Menga ta zira kwallo ta hanyar 1-0 ga tawagar da ba ta da dangantaka da Steven Gerrard a Livingstone.
A lokacin da ake neman nasarar farko a kan hanya tun bayan doke St Johnstone 4-1 a watan Fabrairu, sai Gary Holt ya kori Gerrard a karo na biyu a wasanni 18 a matsayin manajan, ya bar kungiyar ta da maki takwas a bayan shugabannin kungiyar ta Ladbrokes, Hearts.
Menga ya zira kwallaye bakwai kafin rabin lokaci kuma Rangers sun rasa wahayi kuma ba su da wata alama ta daidaitawa.
Yayin da Rangers yanzu suka fadi zuwa matsayi na shida, Livingstone ya tashi zuwa na uku a baya Hibernian a kan raga.
Kuma akwai yiwuwar samun matsala ga Rangers bayan da Calum Spence ya sha wahala daga ciwon kai bayan da aka jefa wani abu a kan baƙi.
Gerrard ya yi canje-canje takwas a tawagar da ta jagoranci Ayr zuwa wasan kusa da karshe na gasar cin kofin Betfred.
A gefe guda kuma, Holt ya ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin 11 da Hearts suka buga a makon da ya gabata kuma zai yi farin ciki da yadda rundunarsa ta yi nasara a kan abokan adawarsu a duk lokacin da suka samu dama.
Rangers na iya zama masu rinjaye a cikin mallakar amma Livingstone ya fi ƙarfin hali lokacin da suke da ita.
Ya kamata su ci kwallo bayan minti biyu da wucewar Menga ya ba Scott Pittman damar cin kwallo ta Allan McGregor amma mai tsaron tsakiya ya rasa damarsa ta hanyar buga kwallo a fili.
Keaghan Jacobs ya yi wani babban fanfo a bayan da ya ga kyaftin Craig Halkett amma abokin aikinsa Alan Lithgow bai iya buga kwallon ba.
Rangers sun kasance suna mulki amma akwai bege fiye da imani a wasan su a cikin wasan karshe.
Alfredo Morelos ya ji ya kamata ya sami tsotse daga cikin taba bayan sa'a 15 bayan da shi da Steven Lawless suka yi wasa amma alƙali Steven Thomson ya ƙi sauraron roko na Colombia.
Rangers sun samu kwallaye biyu a raga a farkon rabin wasan amma sai da suka samu nasarar cin kwallo a hannun dan wasan Ibrox Liam Kelly.
Ko da yake Livi ta ci gaba da wasan bayan minti 34, babu wanda zai iya jayayya cewa sun cancanci kawai saboda aikin da suka yi.
Duk da haka, Rangers da kuma magance Jacobs ta zurfin play da tsare-tsaren.
Scott Arfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya ba da belin ga Scott Robinson, wanda ya damu yayin da yake wucewa zuwa Menga don kammala sauƙi.
Gerrard ya yi kama da ƙwanƙwasawa lokacin da ya canza Coulibaly ga Ryan Kent kuma kusan canjin ya yi tasiri a kan mai tsaron gidan da ya wuce zuwa Morelos amma Kelly ya gudu daga layinsa don toshe shi.
Amma Livingston ya ci gaba da tilasta wa baƙi su yi wasa irin wasan da suke jin daɗi, tare da Lithgow da Halkett suna karɓar dogon lokaci bayan dogon lokaci.
Holt zai iya ƙarawa a cikin minti na ƙarshe amma McGregor ya tashi da kyau don dakatar da Jacobs kafin Lithgow ta rasa fansa daga kusurwa.
Rangers mai kula da Glenn Middleton ya sake neman karin kumallo bayan da ya yi karo da Jacobs amma Thomson ya sake watsi da bukatar.
