Mako guda bayan da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta buga wata sanarwa mai shafi hudu a jaridar Amurka ta yau da kullum da ke tallata cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, ofishin jakadancin Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da manema labaran Amurka don yada farfaganda.
A ranar Laraba da ta gabata ne shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana game da wani shafi na jaridar China Daily a jaridar Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi kowanne a jihar Iowa - bayan da kasar Sin ta zargi kasar Sin da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dokokin Amurka na ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zargin da kasar Sin ta musanta.
Jami'an Amurka sun shaida wa Reuters cewa zargin Trump na cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka wani mataki ne na kara matsa lamba daga Washington kan kasar Sin.
Ko da yake al'ada ce ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su sanya sanarwa don inganta cinikayya, a halin yanzu Beijing da Washington suna fama da yakin cinikayya wanda ya haifar da kasashen biyu sun sanya haraji kan shigo da juna.
An tsara takunkumin cinikin kasar Sin tun farkon yakin cinikayya don yin amfani da masu fitar da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa wadanda ke goyon bayan Jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump, in ji masana Amurka da China.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
Branstad ya rubuta a wata kasida a Des Moines Register ranar Lahadi, "Yanzu kasar Sin ta tabbatar da wannan cin zarafin ta hanyar tallata tallan farfaganda a cikin 'yan jaridunmu".
"A cikin yada farfagandar sa, gwamnatin kasar Sin tana amfani da muhimman al'adun Amurka na 'yancin magana da' yancin manema labarai ta hanyar sanya sanarwa da suka biya a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register", Branstad ya rubuta.
"A akasin wannan, a cikin gidan jaridar da ke kan titi a Beijing, zai yi wuya a sami muryoyin adawa kuma ba za ku ga ainihin ra'ayoyin da jama'ar kasar Sin ke da shi game da mummunan tsarin tattalin arzikin kasar ba, saboda jaridar ta kasance a karkashin jam'iyyar kwaminisanci ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
