Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a ta kashe, in ji jami'ai, tare da yiwuwar adadin wadanda suka mutu ya karu.
Tare da katse sadarwa, jami'an ceto ba su iya samun wani bayani daga hasashen Donggala ba, wani yanki a arewacin Palu wanda ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasa mai girman 7.5.
A birnin Palu, mutane fiye da 16,000 ne suka rasa muhallansu sakamakon girgizar kasar.
Ga wasu abubuwa game da Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Central Sulawesi ne, a ƙarshen wani ƙarancin bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da yawan jama'a 379,800 a 2017.
Garin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da haihuwa lokacin da girgizar kasa da tsunami suka afku.
Donggala wani yanki ne mai nisa wanda ya kai nisan kilomita 300 (180 miles) na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Hasashen, yanki na gudanarwa a ƙarƙashin lardi, yana da maƙasudin yawan jama'a 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Kifi da noma sune manyan masu ci gaba da tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala na bakin teku.
Har ila yau, hakar ma'adinai na da mahimmanci a lardin, amma yawancin wannan aikin yana faruwa a Morowali, a bakin tekun a gefen tsibirin.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, in ji Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya lalata ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami kuma ya afku a yammacin Donggala a shekarar 1996, inda ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana zaune a kan Pacific Ocean seismic Circle kuma ana girgizar ƙasa akai-akai.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Wani mummunar girgizar kasa a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ya haifar da tsunami wanda ya afkawa kasashe 14, ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, kuma fiye da rabin wadanda suka mutu a Aceh.
2005: A karshen watan Maris da farkon watan Afrilu, manyan girgizar ƙasa sun afku a gabar yammacin Sumatra.
Daruruwan sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a gabar tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 6.8 ta afku a kudancin Java, tsibirin da ya fi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afkawa gabar teku ta kudu, ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta afku kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai, a bakin tekun Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai zurfin mita 10 wanda ya lalata ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afku a Pidie Jaya a Aceh, ta haifar da bala'i da firgici yayin da mutane ke tunawa da girgizar kasa da tsunami mai hatsari a shekarar 2004.
Ba a haifar da tsunami a wannan lokacin ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu saboda faduwar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok da ke ƙasar Indonesia, kuma ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, yawancinsu a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon bude ido a can na ɗan lokaci.
An kama babban dan Sarah Palin kan zargin cin zarafin mata
Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska da kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, an kama shi ne kan zargin cin zarafi.
An kama Palin, mai shekaru 29 daga Wasilla, Alaska, a kan zargin cin zarafin gida, keta dokar bayar da rahoton cin zarafin gida da kuma kin amincewa da kama shi, a cewar wani rahoto da 'yan sanda na jihar Alaska suka fitar a ranar Asabar.
A cewar rahoton 'yan sanda, lokacin da wata mata ta san shi yana kokarin kiran' yan sanda don bayar da rahoton laifukan da ake zargi, sai ta dauki wayarta daga gare shi.
Palin yana tsare a gidan yari a Mat-Su Concentration Complex kuma an tsare shi a kan $500 ba tare da kariya ba, a cewar KTUU.
Ya bayyana a kotu a ranar Asabar, inda ya ce shi baƙo ne, ya tabbatar da hakan lokacin da aka tambaye shi inda yake, a cewar hanyar sadarwa.
Palin yana fuskantar tuhume-tuhume uku na laifin aikata laifi na Class A, wanda ke nufin zai iya fuskantar ɗaurin kurkuku har zuwa shekara guda da kuma tara dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin aikata laifi na Class B, wanda ake yankewa hukuncin kisa na kwana daya a gidan yari da kuma tara dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shine karo na farko da aka gabatar da tuhumar aikata laifi a kan Palin ba.
A watan Disamba na 2017, an zarge shi da kai hari ga mahaifinsa, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa, Sarah Palin, ta kira 'yan sanda don sanar da zargin da ake yi.
A halin yanzu ana gabatar da karar ne a gaban kotun tsoffin sojoji ta Alaska.
A shekarar 2016, an tuhume shi da aikata laifin cin zarafin mata, da keta dokar bayar da rahoto kan aikata laifukan cin zarafin mata, da kuma mallakar makami mai guba a cikin hadin gwiwa da lamarin.
Ƙaunarsa ta ce ya ba ta wata alama a fuskarta.
Sarah Pilan ta fuskanci sukar tsoffin sojoji a 2016 bayan da ta danganta halin barazanar ɗanta da PTSD wanda ya samo asali daga lokacin da yake aiki a Iraki.
Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a Indonesia:An kashe daruruwan mutane
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu bayan da wata girgizar kasa ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a.
Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta haddasa tsunami kuma ta halaka dubban gidaje.
An katse hanyoyin sadarwa da wutar lantarki kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
Girgizar ta afku ne a yankin Sulawesi, da ke arewa maso gabashin babban birnin kasar Indonesia, Jakarta.
An raba bidiyo a kafofin sada zumunta da ke nuna lokacin taron.
Mutane da yawa sun taru don su yi biki a bakin teku a birnin Palu sa'ad da tsunami ya auku.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun bukaci a yankewa mutumin da ake zargi da kai harin New York City hukunci mai tsauri
Masu gabatar da kara a New York suna neman a yankewa Sayfullo Saipov hukuncin kisa mafi muni, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York City wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa jihar ba saboda aikata laifi na tarayya tun 1953.
Ana zargin Saipov, mai shekara 30, da amfani da wata motar haya daga Home Depot don kai hari kan hanyar keke a kan Western Avenue a Lower Manhattan, yana buga masu tafiya da masu hawa keke a cikin watan Oktoba.
Don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saipov ya kashe mutane takwas da gangan kuma ya haifar da mummunan rauni ga jiki, bisa ga sanarwar niyyar neman hukuncin kisa, wanda aka shigar a Kudancin New York.
Dukkanin kotunan biyu na iya yanke hukuncin kisa, a cewar takardar kotun.
Makonni bayan harin, wata kotun tarayya ta tuhumi Saipov da laifin aikata laifuka 22 da suka hada da laifin kisan kai don yaudara, laifin da ake amfani da shi a cikin masu gabatar da kara a cikin laifuka masu zaman kansu, da kuma laifin tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci "shirye-shiryen da aka yi da kuma shirin da aka yi", suna mai bayyana harin Saipov a matsayin "mai cin hanci da rashawa, mai zalunci da lalata".
Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya haifar da rauni, lalacewa da asarar dangin dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco, da kuma abokansa, "in ji sanarwar.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma sun shude tun lokacin da New York ta Kudu ta gabatar da hukuncin kisa.
An yanke wa mai laifin, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa na kashe masu sayar da miyagun kwayoyi biyu amma an yanke masa hukuncin kisa a watan Satumbar 2009.
A shekarar 1953 ne aka yanke hukuncin kisa a wani shari'ar tarayya a New York, a kan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka yanke wa hukuncin kisa bayan an same su da laifin shirya leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe su biyu a cikin kujera na lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, dan kasar Uzbekistan, bai nuna nadama ba a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
Ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗin abin da ya yi, in ji 'yan sanda.
Saipov ya shaida wa hukumomi cewa an yi wahayi zuwa gare shi don kai harin bayan kallon bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa, a cewar rahoton.
Ya kuma nemi a sanya tutar ISIS a dakin sa a asibitin, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a kan tuhumar da ake masa da laifin aikata laifuka 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin masu kare Saipov ya ce sun yi takaici da hukuncin da aka yanke.
"Mun yi imanin cewa yanke shawarar neman mafi girman hukunci maimakon karɓar hukuncin rai da rai a kurkuku ba tare da yiwuwar samun 'yanci ba kawai yana ƙara ɓarna da waɗannan abubuwan da suka faru ga duk waɗanda ke da hannu", in ji Patton.
Kungiyar kare Saipov ta riga ta nemi masu gabatar da kara da kada su nemi a yanke masa hukunci mai tsauri.
