Warren da gaske game da neman shugaban kasa
Elizabeth Warren, wata 'yar majalisar dattijai ta Amurka ta ce za ta yi la'akari da batun neman shugaban kasa bayan zaben watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ce dan Democrat din daga Massachusetts ya yi magana game da makomar sa a yayin taron wani gari a yammacin Massachusetts a ranar Asabar.
Warren, wanda ke yawan sukar Donald Trump, yana neman sake zaɓe a watan Nuwamba a kan Geoff Diehl, Wakilin Jiha na GOP, wanda ya jagoranci kamfen na Massachusetts Trump a 2016.
Akwai jita-jita da yawa game da ita cewa za ta iya yin hamayya da Trump a 2020.
A taron da aka yi a Holyoke a ranar Asabar da yamma, ta gana da masu jefa kuri'a a karo na 36 da ta yi amfani da tsarin ko birni tun lokacin da Trump ya hau mulki.
Wani da ke wurin ya tambaye ta ko tana son zama shugabar kasa.
