Ƙungiyar Elite: Dundee Stars 5-3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya zira kwallaye biyu a raga a wasan da Giants suka yi da Dundee
Dundee Stars sun yi daidai da rashin nasara a gasar Elite a ranar Juma'a a kan Belfast Giants ta hanyar lashe wasan 5-3 a Dundee a ranar Asabar.
Giants sun ci gaba da farawa yayin da Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beuvillier suka zira kwallaye biyu.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun yi nasarar daidaitawa da kungiyar gida kafin Dwyer ya sake dawo da nasarar Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya zira kwallo a raga a raga a wasan Dundee kafin Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya ci kwallo biyu a raga.
Wannan ne karo na uku da 'yan Adam Keefe suka yi rashin nasara a gasar Elite a wannan kakar, wanda suka doke Dundee 2-1 a Belfast a ranar Juma'a.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na hudu da kungiyoyin biyu suka hadu a wannan kakar, inda Giants suka doke wasansu uku da suka gabata.
Dwyer ya fara bugawa a minti na hudu a 3:35 tare da taimakon Kendall McFaull, tare da David Rutherford yana taimakawa yayin da Beauvillier ya ninka ci a minti hudu daga baya.
A cikin lokacin budewa, Sullivan ya dawo da wasansa a 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya taimaka ya samar da kwallo mai daidaitawa na Cownie a 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da cewa Giants sun ci gaba a cikin hutu na farko yayin da ya zira kwallaye na biyu a ƙarshen dare a ƙarshen farkon.
Ƙungiyar gida ta sake haɗuwa kuma, sake, Bouchard ya tabbatar da cewa suna da daidaituwa tare da burin da ya dace a 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun hada kai don taimakawa Nielsen ya ba Dundee nasara a wasan farko a ƙarshen rabi na biyu kuma ya tabbatar da nasara ta hanyar zura kwallo ta biyar a tsakiyar rabin.
Giants, wadanda yanzu suka rasa wasanni hudu daga cikin biyar da suka gabata, suna wasa a gida da Milton Keynes a wasan su na gaba ranar Juma'a.
Wani Mai Kula da Jiragen Sama Ya Mutu Domin Ya Tabbatar Da Cewa Daruruwan Mutane Suna Tserewa Daga Girgizar Kasa
An yi wa wani mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama a Indonesia lakabi da jarumi bayan ya mutu yana tabbatar da cewa jirgin da ke dauke da daruruwan mutane ya tashi lafiya daga kasa.
Mutane fiye da 800 ne suka mutu, kuma da yawa sun bata bayan wata babbar girgizar kasa ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi a ranar Juma'a, inda ta haifar da tsunami.
Ƙarƙashin ƙasa mai ƙarfi yana ci gaba da buga yankin kuma mutane da yawa sun makale a cikin duwatsu a birnin Bulus.
Amma duk da cewa abokan aikinsa sun gudu don rayukansu, ɗan shekara 21 mai suna Anthonius Gunawan Agung ya ƙi barin aikinsa a cikin babban tashar jirgin sama mai kyau a filin jirgin saman Palu, Mutiara Sis Al Jufri.
Ya tsaya a can don tabbatar da cewa jirgin Batik Air Flight 6321, wanda ke kan titin jirgin a lokacin, zai iya tashi lafiya.
Sa'an nan kuma ya yi tsalle daga cikin kula da zirga-zirga hasumiya a lokacin da ya yi tunani shi ne fadowa.
