Yadda za a Amurka-China cinikayya yaki zama pro-Beijing
Wa'azin farko na yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China ya isa ya makantar da mutum, kuma yayin da yakin bai ƙare ba, rikice-rikice tsakanin ƙasashen na iya zama da amfani ga Beijing a cikin dogon lokaci, in ji masana.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya ba da gargadin farko a wannan shekara ta hanyar sanya haraji kan manyan kayayyakin da China ke fitarwa ciki har da bangarorin hasken rana, karfe da kuma aluminium.
An gabatar da mafi girman ci gaba a wannan makon tare da sabbin haraji da ke shafar abubuwa masu darajar dala biliyan 200 (£150 biliyan), suna biyan haraji, ga dukkan dalilai, rabin duk kayan da ke shigowa Amurka daga China.
Beijing ta biya diyyar a kowane lokaci, kuma, kwanan nan, ta sanya haraji daga kashi biyar zuwa goma bisa dari kan kayayyakin Amurka biliyan 600.
China ta yi alkawarin yin daidai da kokarin Amurka kuma ba ita kadai babbar tattalin arzikin duniya da za ta yi kasa a gwiwa ba da jimawa ba.
Samun Washington ta daina nufin mika wuya ga bukatun, amma nuna rashin amincewar jama'a ga Amurka zai jawo wa shugaban kasar Sin Xi Jinping kunya sosai.
Duk da haka, masana sun ce idan Beijing ta iya yin tafiya daidai, matsin lambar yakin cinikayya na Amurka na iya tallafawa China a cikin dogon lokaci ta hanyar tabbatar da cewa tattalin arzikin biyu ba su dogara da juna ba.
"Gaskiyar cewa yanke shawara na siyasa cikin sauri a Washington ko Beijing na iya haifar da yanayin da zai haifar da fargabar tattalin arziki a cikin ƙasa ɗaya ko wata, a zahiri, ya fi haɗari fiye da yadda masu lura da su suka riga suka gane", in ji Abigail Grace, mai bincike mai alaƙa da ke mai da hankali kan Asiya a Cibiyar Tsaro ta Sabuwar Amurka, wanda ke da irin wannan tattaunawar.
Syria ta shirya ta karbi 'yan gudun hijira, in ji Ministan Harkokin Waje
Syria ta ce a shirye take ta karɓi masu neman mafaka a kan son rai kuma tana neman taimako don sake gina ƙasar da ta lalace a yaƙi na shekaru bakwai.
Da yake jawabi ga Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Waje Walid al-Moualem ya ce yanayi na inganta a kasar.
"Yanayin a kasa ya fi karko da tsaro yanzu, godiya ga yaki da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na aiki tukuru wajen gyara yankunan da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata don dawo da al'amura cikin sauki.
Yanayin yanzu ya dace don karɓar masu neman mafaka da suka dawo gida bayan sun gudu daga ta'addanci da kuma matakan tattalin arziki masu cutarwa waɗanda ke nufin rayuwarsu ta yau da kullun da kuma rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa 'yan Syria sama da miliyan 5.5 sun tsere daga kasar tun lokacin da yakin ya fara a 2011.
Mutane miliyan shida da ke zaune a kasar na bukatar agaji.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta yi maraba da taimako don sake gina kasar.
Amma ya jaddada cewa ba zai karbi taimako ba tare da wasu sharudda ko taimako daga kasashen da suka goyi bayan 'yan tawaye.
Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin duniya a Paris
Kungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar cin kofin Ryder ta 2018 ta doke Kungiyar Amurka da 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Le Golf National a bayan Paris, Faransa.
USA ta sha kaye sau shida a jere a Turai, kuma ba ta lashe gasar cin kofin Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sami nasarar cin nasara yayin da Thomas Bjorn, kyaftin din Denmark, ya kai maki 14.5 da ake buƙata don doke Amurka.
Phil Mickelson ya yi wasa mai wuya, amma lokacin da kwallon tauraruwar Amurka ta sauka a cikin ruwa a rami na 16th par-3 sai ya mika wasan ga Francesco Molinari.
Molinari, wani dan wasan golf na Italiya, ya yi fice a kowane zagaye, ya zama 1 cikin 'yan wasa 4 da suka ci 5-0-0 tun lokacin da gasar ta canza zuwa tsarin ta na yanzu a 1979.
An yi wa dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth 5&4 da dan wasan da ya fi dacewa a kan takarda a Turai, Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Babban dan wasan duniya, Dustin Johnson, ya rasa 2&1 ga Ian Poulter na Ingila wanda ya fi dacewa a wasan karshe na Ryder Cup.
A wasan da ya buga a gasar cin kofin Ryder ta takwas, dan wasan Spain Sergio Garcia ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasan da suka fi nasara a tarihin gasar da ya zira kwallaye 25.5 a wasan.
"Ba ni da daya zuwa kuka kullum, amma ba zan iya taimaka cewa a yau.
Ta kasance mai wuya shekara.
Ina godiya ga Thomas da ya zaɓe ni kuma ya sa bangaskiya a cikina.
Ina farin ciki, farin ciki da cewa mun samu da kofin baya.
Tawagar tana da mahimmanci, kuma ina farin cikin taimaka", in ji Garcia cikin hawaye bayan nasarar Turai.
Ya mika wa dan kasarsa John Ram kwallo kuma ya doke zakaran golf na Amurka, Tiger Woods, 2&1 a wasan da aka buga a ranar Lahadi.
Rahm, ɗan shekara 23 ya ce: "Na yi alfahari da na doke Tiger Woods domin na girma ina kallon yadda yake wasan golf.
Woods ya rasa dukkan wasanninsa hudu a Faransa, wanda hakan ya sa rikodin Ryder Cup ya kasance 13-21-3.
Kuma wannan adadi ne mai ban mamaki ga daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasa a duniya, wanda ya lashe kofin duniya 14 a rayuwarsa, na biyu kawai ga Jack Nicklaus.
Sai dai Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau da suka taka rawar gani a duk lokacin gasar, Team USA ta yi ta gwagwarmaya a duk tsawon karshen mako don samun hanyar da ta dace.
Kocin Amurka Jim Furyk ya ce bayan rashin nasarar da tawagarsa ta yi, "Ina alfahari da wannan kungiya, za su yi gwagwarmaya sosai.
Mun sanya matsa lamba a kan Turai a lokacin da safe.
Mun yi yaƙi.
Dole ne ku ba da yabo ga Thomas.
Shi ne kyaftin ba tare da biyu.
Dukkanin 'yan wasan 12 sun yi wasa sosai.
Zan yi aiki tare da PGA na Amurka da kuma kwamitin gasar Ryder Cup.
Ina son 'yan wasanmu 12 kuma ina alfahari da kasancewa kyaftin din su.
Dole ne ka yi musu wani abu.
Sun yi wasa fiye da mu".
